BaDoPi is the Barcelona's Free Software Users Groups. It means ''Barcelona's Penguin Tamers'' in catalan ''*Ba*//rcelonins'' /*Do*//madors de/ ''*Pi*//ngüins'', or in spanish ''*Ba*//rceloneses'' /*Do*//madores de/ ''*Pi*//ngüinos''. RMS dislikes our name :( but it's only a joke, our members use a wide range of free OS :)

You can learn more about us, or read or articles (usually in spanish or catalan) on http://www.badopi.org, you also can subscribe to our mailing list by web http://lists.badopi.org/mailman/listinfo/comandob or by mail comandob-request@badopi.org with subject "subscribe".
